		## ğŸ”§ 7. Troubleshooting {#troubleshooting}
		
		### Lá»—i ThÆ°á»ng Gáº·p:
		
		#### A. ChromeDriver KhÃ´ng TÆ°Æ¡ng ThÃ­ch
		```
		Error: SessionNotCreatedException: session not created
		```
		**Giáº£i phÃ¡p:**
		```java
		// Cáº­p nháº­t WebDriverManager
		WebDriverManager.chromedriver().clearDriverCache().setup();
		```
		
		#### B. Element KhÃ´ng TÃ¬m Tháº¥y
		```
		Error: NoSuchElementException: no such element
		```
		**Giáº£i phÃ¡p:**
		```java
